GETPACIFIST

NAME
        GetPacifist()

SYNOPSIS
        int GetPacifist()

DESCRIPTION
        The default, 0, means the creature is willing to engage in combat. A return of 1 means the creature will not fight, regardless of whether it is under attack.

EXAMPLES
         

LOCATION
        /lib/body


SEE ALSO
        SetPacifist

Author
        Cratylus

